                        <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/society/2006/jan/24/health.lifeandhealth?INTCMP=ILCNETTXT3487">Stressed out over cerebral climaxes</a>
                    </p>
                </li><li>
                    <p class="t6 web-publication-date">6 Jun 2012</p>
                    <p class="t7">
                        <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/shortcuts/2012/jun/06/exercise-beat-depression-research?INTCMP=ILCNETTXT3487">I believe exercise can help people beat depression</a>
                    </p>
                </li><li>
                    <p class="t6 web-publication-date">22 Feb 2011</p>
                    <p class="t7">
                        <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2011/feb/22/luisa-dillner-guide-marriage-and-health?INTCMP=ILCNETTXT3487">Dr Luisa Dillner's guide to . . . Marriage and health</a>
                    </p>
                </li>

            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>  
  
